{
  "stem": "6944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By then I already had very good command of French, because I had the grammar behind me, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother was a char.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that is how we pushed along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember one day, we were sitting together at supper time, and there was some meat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was very hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother-- I had finished my plate-- my portion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother took her meat and put it in my plate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I thought, oh, I protested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Come on, come on, she says, I'm not hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't need it, and I ate it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she was left with bones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I still remember, and I have a conscience about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I haven't got a conscience about many, many things but that I have a conscience still until today.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[COUGHS] And so we lived a frugal life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, one day my father had to go to extend his passport, his Polish passport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He didn't have the sense to get a German passport at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyhow, he comes to the-- you come into the Polish Embassy or consulate, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You have to hand in your passport if you want it extended.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You pay the fee and you wait, because there are so many hundreds of other people there to be attended to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Well, I don't know how long it took, but after a certain while the name is called out and then you take your passport, you go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because you already have paid, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They make sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that is right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So his name was called out, Erder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He goes, takes his passport and wants to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When all of a sudden somebody taps him on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he turns around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He sees a stranger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, are you Erder from Cologne?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
